item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:

WHAT YOU’LL DO

  • Be the hands-on leader for our hard-working SF-based Accounts Payable team
  • Oversee the team’s execution of accurate, timely payment for:
    • hundreds of thousands of domestic driver-partners each week via ACH
    • hundreds of vendor payments each week
    • hundreds of employee expense reports each week
  • Drive AP’s deliverables in our monthly accounting close process (including journals and reconciliations)
  • Serve as primary escalation point for US-based AP related issues
  • Hire and train new team members as needed
  • Be metrics-driven in the management of your team’s work, while never losing focus on the human element present in all great teams
  • Proactively ensure that AP’s processes evolve as our company scales, specifically with a focus on automation and controls
  • Drive innovation, be resourceful and creative to find efficiency
  • Represent AP’s needs as we complete our Oracle implementation and future systems implementations
  • Drive AP’s needs in ad-hoc projects as required

 

WHAT YOU’LL NEED

  • 10+ years experience in Accounts Payable and/or Finance/Accounting roles
  • Experience at a large company (scale/volume) and a fast-growing tech company (adaptability, hands-on process optimization) is ideal.  Experience in a multi-entity structure preferred
  • Leadership style and dedication that inspires your team
  • Strong understanding of GAAP, allocations, reconciliations, and AP’s role in the monthly accounting close
  • Strong Excel, ability to work with large sets of data efficiently
  • Thrive under pressure, always get the job done, enjoy our dynamic environment
  • Experience with Oracle R12 strongly preferred.  Bill.com and Expensify also nice to have
  • Empowered, problem-solver attitude.  Not only do you get it done in a crunch, but you work proactively with others to build a better process for next time around
  • College degree or equivalent work experience
  • Great communication and people skills - people need to know they will always get clear, accurate information from you
  • Excellent eye for detail - balanced with swift execution.  We need to do things quickly and we need to do them well.  Balancing those can be challenging and this should be a strength of yours
  • Hustle and a passion for Accounts Payable, Uber, and the problems we are solving

 

PERKS

  • Employees are showered with Uber credits each month
  • Ground floor opportunity with the team; shape the strategic direction of the company
  • The rare opportunity to change the world such that everyone around you is using the product you built
  • We’re not just another social web app, we’re moving real people and assets and reinventing transportation and logistics globally
  • Sharp, motivated co-workers in a fun office environment  

BENEFITS (U.S.)

  • 401(k) plan, gym reimbursement, nine paid company holidays
  • Full medical/dental/vision package to fit your needs
  • Unlimited vacation policy; work hard and take time when you need it

item.title: Ajax Grid Shortcode
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row css=".vc_custom_1415829592009{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;}"][vc_column width="3/4" css=".vc_custom_1423487367730{background-color: #ffffff !important;}"][pftext_separator title="Point Finder Ajax Grid Shortcode" title_align="separator_align_left"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4" el_class="col-sm-4"][vc_single_image image="529" border_color="grey" img_link_large="yes" img_link_target="_self" img_size="medium" el_class="prettyPhoto" css=".vc_custom_1423633905289{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="3/4" el_class="col-sm-8"][vc_column_text]By using “PF Ajax Grid” element which can easily be added through Visual Composer, you can create your items that you have added to PointFinder. If you wish, you can filter listing categories or other taxonomies. You can list only the "Featured" items or ensure that only the items that you have defined are displayed.
You can determine the number of columns, sort by criteria and filter options as you wish. And you can perform all these with a couple of mouse curser moves.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_empty_space height="22px"][vc_separator color="grey" style="double"][vc_empty_space height="22px"][pf_itemgrid orderby="title" sortby="ASC" items="6" cols="3" grid_layout_mode="fitRows" filters="true" itemboxbg="#f2f2f2"][vc_empty_space height="22px"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_widget_sidebar sidebar_id="eb3670fcb4965f5007d73f8c63a9f195"][/vc_column][/vc_row]

You can determine the number of columns, sort by criteria and filter options as you wish. item.title: Features
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: [vc_row css=".vc_custom_1423485814431{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}" widthopt="" fixedbg="" footerrow=""][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="1238" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Quick Setup" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can perform the setup of your theme in minutes. Moreover, you can choose any of our demo websites and create it exactly the same.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Front End Upload System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can make sure your visitors upload to your website with this system. You can allow them to upload either for free or you can determine a price per item. You can make additional pricing in special listings with Featured Points feature.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Paypal Recurring and Direct Payments" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]Thanks to Point Finder’s system which is fully integrated with Paypal, you can allow your visitors to choose Paypal Recurring or Paypal Direct Payment options when uploading their items. In addition to that, you can also run your system with bank transfer option and offline payment mode.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Paypal IPN System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can leave the tracking of processes such as cancellation and stopping of agreement in Recurring Payments to Point Finder IPN system. In such cases, it will make instantaneous changes in the system, saving you a lot of work.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Order Tracking System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]Point Finder tracks every payment that is due and presents you a detailed report. You can track payments and processes for any items your users have uploaded to your system.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1422536038507{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}" widthopt="" fixedbg="" footerrow=""][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Customizable Info Windows" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can customize information windows which open when you click on points with this feature. You can adjust their color, size and content as you like from the admin panel.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Customizable Points" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can create your points easily without making any uploads, either for categories or for each item, thanks to Custom Point Config feature that we offer to you.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Multiple Point at Same Place" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can easily add with this system which has been made for multiple items located at the same address and show your visitors all of them.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Geolocation feature" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]We used Google Map Geolocation feature in Point Finder to the best of our ability. You can position your visitors, and easily show your properties or items in specified distance.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Map Styling" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can create personalized maps on Point Finder Google Map by styling. You can find detailed information on how to do that from our help documentation.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Map Clusters" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can group crowded cluster points with Google Map Cluster feature and adjust the characteristics of these groups with administration panel.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="1237" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large" alignment="right"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1422531067120{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}" widthopt="" fixedbg="" footerrow=""][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="1239" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Ajax Features" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can make different selections in systems with many points thanks to Point Finder AJAX infrastructure. For example, you can ensure that only points which is being displayed are loaded and these points are increased when changing area. Loading when you zoom in or zoom out in your map is another feature you can use in this section.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Well Documented" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can access all information about Point Finder with our help documentation. You can review our easy-to-understand documentation with step-by-step setup description online.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Social Login System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can make sure that users who want to register to your website do this easily through Facebook and Twitter. You can also facilitate their log-ins with this method.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Mail Template System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can customize many e-mails which are sent to your users and the admin with Point Finder mail system. You can configure SMTP infrastructure from this system and change many features, such as colors of the email theme..[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Favorites System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can allow your visitors to add the items they like into their favorites with this system.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Review System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can activate a review system for your items without using any additional plugins. You can create your own review system with separate voting option for any amount of criteria that you like.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1422536038507{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}" widthopt="" fixedbg="" footerrow=""][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Visual Composer Page Builder" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can use the existing Visual Composer elements and Point Finder special shortcuts which are added by us thanks to our theme which uses the latest version of Visual composer. With this, you can create your pages without writing any lines just by clicking and dragging with your mouse. You can use the shortcuts we created for you beforehand with Templatera, which is a Visual Composer plugin and comes with our theme.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Customizable Item Details" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can create information fields that you want in your item details with Point Finder. Without being dependant on previously defined fields and writing any line of code, you can create rich content by click and drag feature.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Customizable Search Area" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can search any criteria in both your maps and search Widgets with Point Finder. You can match search criteria with any Custom Fields that you enter and create a search system that is completely customized by you.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Claim/Report Listing System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can create a claim system for the items that you and your visitors uploaded and get opinions from the users who visit your website.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: [vc_row css=".vc_custom_1423485814431{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}" widthopt="" fixedbg="" footerrow=""][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="1238" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Quick Setup" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can perform the setup of your theme in minutes. Moreover, you can choose any of our demo websites and create it exactly the same.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Front End Upload System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can make sure your visitors upload to your website with this system. You can allow them to upload either for free or you can determine a price per item. You can make additional pricing in special listings with Featured Points feature.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Paypal Recurring and Direct Payments" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]Thanks to Point Finder’s system which is fully integrated with Paypal, you can allow your visitors to choose Paypal Recurring or Paypal Direct Payment options when uploading their items. In addition to that, you can also run your system with bank transfer option and offline payment mode.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Paypal IPN System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can leave the tracking of processes such as cancellation and stopping of agreement in Recurring Payments to Point Finder IPN system. In such cases, it will make instantaneous changes in the system, saving you a lot of work.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Order Tracking System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]Point Finder tracks every payment that is due and presents you a detailed report. You can track payments and processes for any items your users have uploaded to your system.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1422536038507{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}" widthopt="" fixedbg="" footerrow=""][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Customizable Info Windows" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can customize information windows which open when you click on points with this feature. You can adjust their color, size and content as you like from the admin panel.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Customizable Points" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can create your points easily without making any uploads, either for categories or for each item, thanks to Custom Point Config feature that we offer to you.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Multiple Point at Same Place" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can easily add with this system which has been made for multiple items located at the same address and show your visitors all of them.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Geolocation feature" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]We used Google Map Geolocation feature in Point Finder to the best of our ability. You can position your visitors, and easily show your properties or items in specified distance.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Map Styling" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can create personalized maps on Point Finder Google Map by styling. You can find detailed information on how to do that from our help documentation.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Map Clusters" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can group crowded cluster points with Google Map Cluster feature and adjust the characteristics of these groups with administration panel.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="1237" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large" alignment="right"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1422531067120{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}" widthopt="" fixedbg="" footerrow=""][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="1239" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Ajax Features" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can make different selections in systems with many points thanks to Point Finder AJAX infrastructure. For example, you can ensure that only points which is being displayed are loaded and these points are increased when changing area. Loading when you zoom in or zoom out in your map is another feature you can use in this section.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Well Documented" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can access all information about Point Finder with our help documentation. You can review our easy-to-understand documentation with step-by-step setup description online.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Social Login System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can make sure that users who want to register to your website do this easily through Facebook and Twitter. You can also facilitate their log-ins with this method.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Mail Template System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can customize many e-mails which are sent to your users and the admin with Point Finder mail system. You can configure SMTP infrastructure from this system and change many features, such as colors of the email theme..[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Favorites System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can allow your visitors to add the items they like into their favorites with this system.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Review System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can activate a review system for your items without using any additional plugins. You can create your own review system with separate voting option for any amount of criteria that you like.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1422536038507{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}" widthopt="" fixedbg="" footerrow=""][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Visual Composer Page Builder" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can use the existing Visual Composer elements and Point Finder special shortcuts which are added by us thanks to our theme which uses the latest version of Visual composer. With this, you can create your pages without writing any lines just by clicking and dragging with your mouse. You can use the shortcuts we created for you beforehand with Templatera, which is a Visual Composer plugin and comes with our theme.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Customizable Item Details" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can create information fields that you want in your item details with Point Finder. Without being dependant on previously defined fields and writing any line of code, you can create rich content by click and drag feature.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Customizable Search Area" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can search any criteria in both your maps and search Widgets with Point Finder. You can match search criteria with any Custom Fields that you enter and create a search system that is completely customized by you.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Claim/Report Listing System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can create a claim system for the items that you and your visitors uploaded and get opinions from the users who visit your website.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Customizable Page Headers" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can create separate headers for each page, or make one header for all pages.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="1317" border_color="grey" Finder is fully compatible with mobiles, and you can run it on any device because it is fully compatible with IOS, Android and other smartphone systems.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space this excellent add-on that comes with Point Finder, you can create sliders as you like.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Google reCaptcha" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" can use this feature in all fields which are available in Point Finder. The latest version of reCaptcha is fully integrated with our theme.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Advanced Theme Options" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]While designing Point Finder, we prepared Options Panels which you can use to customize every detail possible and you can use it to check all points in your website. You can solve all your questions and problems with the detail panel documentation.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Custom Widgets" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can list the latest items or featured items easily with special Widgets we designed for you. You can make searches within the page or add your tweets from Twitter easily.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1422878182085{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 80px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}" widthopt="" fixedbg="" footerrow=""][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="WPML Support" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]Point Finder gives you the chance to use your website with multiple language option thanks to its WPML support. As you can see from online help documentation, you can easily translate all words in your website to any language you like.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading
